<h6><a href="#Page Contents"><font color="#800000"><strong><img
src="images/upa.gif" border="0" width="15" height="11"></strong></font></a>
End of Quality Summary of 1995 USA Upland Crop</h6>
<hr>
<p><strong>Description:</strong> <font color="#800000"><strong>Quality
Summary of 1995 and 1994 USA Upland Crops ~ </strong></font>This
page includes the document contents and the first of five
sections of a document entitled <font color="#800000">1995 Crop
Final Report: USA Cotton Quality Measurements and Analysis</font>,
compiled several times a year by the staff of Cotton
Incorporated's Fiber Quality Research Division, available to the
cotton community.</p>
