<DOCNO>WT24-B31-24</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA068-000423-B023-93</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.masdef.org:80/serv/nlg.html 166.84.57.84 19970113072924 text/html 1631
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
