</DOCHDR>
<HTML> <HEAD><TITLE>Demonstrator's Site: The National Lawyer's Guild</TITLE></HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#FF0000" VLINK="#D90000" ALINK="#FFFF00"><CENTER><TABLE WIDTH=500><TR><TD><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="../gifs/servbut.gif" ALT="SERVICES" HEIGHT=100 WIDTH=90><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="../gifs/nlgban.gif" ALT="THE NATIONAL LAWYERS GUILD" HEIGHT=100 WIDTH=410 HSPACE=0><P></TD></TR><TR><TD><BLOCKQUOTE>The National Lawyers Guild is a national bar association for lawyers, law students, jailhouse lawyers and other legal workers.  It was formed in 1937 to provide an alternative to the all-white, anti-labor and anti-New Deal conventional bar associations.  Since then, the Guild's lawyers have fought for unions and workers, persons suspected by the Joe McCarthy-led Congress of being "Un-American", the civil rights movement in the South, anti-war protesters, pro-choice proponents, immigrants and many others.<P><UL>	<LI><B><FONT SIZE="4"><a href="guildacts.html">Activities and Publications</A><P>	<LI><a href="guildhis.html">A Brief History</A><P>	<LI><A HREF="contnlg.html">Contacting the NLG</A><P></FONT></B></UL></BLOCKQUOTE></TD></TR><TR><TD ALIGN=CENTER><HR><A HREF="../index.html"><IMG SRC="../gifs/homebar.gif" ALT="HOME" BORDER=0 HSPACE=5></A><A HREF="../serv/masdef.html"><IMG SRC="../gifs/masdbar.gif" ALT="THE MASS DEFENSE COMMITTEE" BORDER=0 HSPACE=5></A></TD></TR></TABLE></CENTER></BODY></HTML>
</DOC>
