<html><head>   <title>Demonstrator's Site</title>   <meta name="GENERATOR" content="Mozilla/2.01Gold (Win32)"></head><body text="#000000" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" link="#FF0000" vlink="#D90000" alink="#FFFF00"><CENTER><table WIDTH=500><tr><td ALIGN=CENTER> <p><img src="gifs/demlogo.gif" lowsrc="gifs/doyoulia.gif" alt="DEMONSTRATOR'S SITE" border=0 ></p>  <p><i><font SIZE=+1>Welcome to the</font></i> </p> <h1>DEMONSTRATOR'S SITE</h1> <p><i><font SIZE=+1>Providing you with the latest news, commentaryand instruction relating to your right to assemble with others and demonstrate.<br><img src="gifs/nlglogo.gif" border=0 ><br></font></i><b><a href="serv/masdef.html">THE MASS DEFENSE COMMITTEE</a></b>of <b><a href="serv/nlg.html">THE NATIONAL LAWYER'S GUILD</a></b> </p>  <p><hr SIZE=1 NOSHADE></p> </td></tr><tr><td><table><tr><td WIDTH=120 ALIGN=LEFT VALIGN=TOP> <p><img src="gifs/newsbut.gif" alt="NEWS" border=0  align=left></p> </td><td WIDTH=400><h3  ><a href="news/reps/index.html">Reports from Demonstrations</a></h3><ul TYPE=CIRCLE> 
