<h3><a href="news/comm/index.html">Commentary</a></h3><ul TYPE=CIRCLE> 
<li>NY Activists Increasingly Experience Substantial Detention</li> 
<li>The Lawyer and the "Bad Food" Sign</li>  
<li>The Anti-Abortion Protester Meets the Stalker Law</li>  
<li>and more ... </li> </ul></td></tr><tr><td COLSPAN=2> <p><hr SIZE=1 NOSHADE></p> </td></tr><tr VALIGN=TOP><td ALIGN=LEFT> <p><img src="gifs/refsbut.gif" alt="REFERENCES" border=0  align=left></p> </td><td><h3  ><a href="refs/manu/index.html">Demonstrator's Manual</a></h3><ul TYPE=CIRCLE> <li>Planning the Demonstration </li>  <li>At the Demonstration </li>  <li>You Are Under Arrest </li>  <li>In Court </li> </ul><h3  ><a href="refs/lega/index.html">Legal Materials</a></h3><ul TYPE=CIRCLE> <li>Court Decisions </li>  <li>Sample Motions </li>  <li>Pertinent Statutes </li> </ul><h3><a href="refs/orgs/index.html">Organizations</a></h3><ul TYPE=CIRCLE> <li>Legal </li>  <li>Political Organizations </li>  <li>Police and Other Government Phone Numbers </li> </ul></td></tr><tr><td COLSPAN=2> <p><hr SIZE=1 NOSHADE></p> </td></tr><tr VALIGN=TOP><td ALIGN=LEFT> <p><img src="gifs/servbut.gif" alt="SERVICES" border=0  align=left></p> </td><td><h3  ><a href="serv/masdef.html">The Mass Defense Committee</a></h3><ul TYPE=CIRCLE> <li>Purpose and History of Committee </li>  <li>Assistance from the Attorney of the Week </li>  <li>Attending Meetings of the Committee </li> </ul><h3  ><a href="serv/nlg.html">The National Lawyers Guild</a></h3><ul TYPE=CIRCLE> <li>Activities and Publications </li>  <li>NLG History </li> </ul></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr ALIGN=CENTER><td> <p><hr SIZE=1 NOSHADE><br><i>Designed and maintained by <a href="mailto:rschmidt@panix.com">RobSchmidt</a> - Graphics by <a href="mailto:rschmidt@panix.com">Luba Lukova</a></i></p> </td></tr></table></CENTER></body></html>
