<H3>Native Forest Council Closing</H3>
<PRE>This message is being forwarded as it is of interest to the entire
environmental community. The NFC fills an important niche and perhaps
someone out there may be of help
-------------------------------------------------------------------
June 19, 1996

Due to a serious funding shortfall the NFC has been forced to layoff our
entire staff and we will probably cease operations at the end of the month
unless a benefactor comes forward, which at this point cannot be
predicted.

We will operate with a skeleton staff for as long as possible and then may
have to cease operations altogether.

>From the bottom of our hearts we thank our many supporters for their
confidence and support during the past eight years.

I am sure that all of us will continue to do all that we can, wherever and
whatever we end up doing, to continue the fight to reject further
compromises in the prtotection and preservation of all that's wild and
free.

Sincerely yours,

Tim Hermach
Founder and Executive Director


