reject Smith's bid for a reprieve from his June 14 execution date.
Smith, who was convicted of murdering an indianapolis police
officer in 1980, is scheduled to be the first person to be executed
by lethal injection in Indiana.
  Police said that Ajabu, Robertson, and Howell sprayed what was
thought to be and accelerate on a u.s. flag and tried to ignite it.
A scuffle brok e out. Officers used pepper spray to subdue them.
Ajabu and the other 2 men were taken to Wishard memorial hospital
before being taken to the Marion County lockup.
