@columbia.eduAddress:  208 HamiltonKathryn B. YatrakisAssociate Dean of Columbia CollegePhone: (212) 854-2441Fax: (212) 854-7984email: kby1@columbia.eduAddress: 208 HamiltonColumbia College Dean's Office(212) 854-2446202 Hamilton Hall                 **This is NOT an April Fools' Joke**</PRE></TD></TR><TR><TD ALIGN=RIGHT><HR><A HREF="index.html"><IMG SRC="../../gifs/backbar.gif" ALT="BACK" BORDER=0></A></TD></TR></TABLE></CENTER></BODY></HTML>
