http://www.masdef.org:80/news/comm/petty=crimes.html 166.84.57.84 19970113083748 text/html 5361
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Mon, 13 Jan 1997 08:37:53 GMT
Server: Apache/1.0.2
Content-type: text/html
