<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Demonstrator's Site: A Message To Activists...</TITLE></HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#FF0000" VLINK="#D90000" ALINK="#FFFF00"><CENTER><TABLE WIDTH=500><TR><TD><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="../../gifs/newsbut.gif" ALT="NEWS" HEIGHT=100 WIDTH=90><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="../../gifs/commban.gif" ALT="Commentary" HEIGHT=100 WIDTH=410 HSPACE=0><P></TD></TR><TR><TD><BLOCKQUOTE><H3>A MESSAGE TO ACTIVISTS...</H3><I>and feminists, socialists, gay-rights activists, environmentalists, labor-rightsactivists, anti-racists, anti-classists, radicals, idealists, and other crazy dreamers...</I><P>from <A HREF="mailto:schissel@math.cornell.edu?subject=Your message to activists">Eric Schissel</A><P><BLOCKQUOTE><B>For so long as you continue to be a good person in a bad society,	you will be vilified.  Keep at it.<p>	You will be slandered.  Only during your lifetime.<p>	You will be called the worst person on Earth by people rather	nearly fitting that description themselves.  Take pride in having 	the right enemies.<p>	Don't let the bastards get you down.</B></BLOCKQUOTE></BLOCKQUOTE></TD></TR><TR><TD ALIGN=RIGHT><HR><A HREF="index.html"><IMG SRC="../../gifs/backbar.gif" ALT="BACK" BORDER=0></A></TD></TR></TABLE></CENTER></BODY></HTML>
