<HEAD>
<TITLE>Joining the Village ...</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<body bgcolor="ffffff" text="000044" link="0000ff" vlink="660099">


<A HREF="index.html">
<img src="home_btn.gif" 
     hspace=5
     align="middle" 
     alt="HOME">

VILLAGE Home Page
</A> 

<p>
<img src="/icons/line_sun.gif" alt="----------">
<p>

<h2>JOINING THE VILLAGE ...</H2><P>

The terms &quot;Home Page&quot; and &quot;Web site&quot; are somewhat confusing in that they seem to be interchangeable. We can set up a Home Page for you at the Traffic Safety Information Village and this will be your unique Web site, with its own address and accessibility on the World Wide Web. <p>

Think of it as a sort of billboard or brochure that describes the products or services that you or your organization have to offer. But in contrast with the brochure, your page will be interactive. And it can potentially be viewed by millions of Net users locally and around the world at very little cost to you. <p>

If you are curious about the potential of the Web for your business or organization, why not try a basic one-page site? Write out what you would like to say on a sheet of paper and we'll put it up for you for a basic $300 cost for one year. This includes a two-year subscription to the Village database.<p>
If your page (site) is interesting and easy to find on the Net, your potential clients will come to you. They can do this by mail, telephone, fax or E-mail. To make it easier, we can put an E-mail form right on screen. Users simply type in their message and hit the send or submit button. Forms for mail and credit card ordering can also be built into your page.<p>

PDE has the expertise to build sophisticated Web sites and offers the advantage of broad knowledge of safety issues and the goal of creating a networked community of interest.<p>

You can have your local internet connection provider set up a Home Page for you and, for a small charge, we can make it a part of the Village by creating a link to it. However, there are advantages to having us set up your page. There are millions of Web pages out there, but by setting up your page with us, you become part of the Net's distinctive traffic safety community. You will also benefit from everything PDE does to publicize the Village resource.<p>

<p>
<img src="/icons/line_sun.gif" alt="----------">
<p>

