<P>
<IMG SRC="marbthin.gif" ALT="------------------------">
<P>
<blockquote>
The Swedish National Road Administration is responsible for all matters in connection with road traffic, including safety, licensing, and record keeping for all license holders in Sweden.<P>

The Drivers License Department is nationally responsible for the licensing of drivers. This includes training curriculum, examinations, and supervision of traffic schools.<P>

