<title>GRADUATED LICENSING-A GROUNDSWELL OF SUPPORT</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor=#ffffff>

<h2>GRADUATED LICENSING-A GROUNDSWELL OF SUPPORT</h2>
<p>"A groundswell of support" for Graduated Driver Licensing and confusion over the definition of GDL
were issues discussed at a recent workshop organized by the U.S.
Transportation Research Board. Concerns were expressed that jurisdictions
changing their licensing systems would not adopt all of the elements
necessary for a GDL system to achieve its crash-reducation potential.
<p>
