<head><title>New Driver Car Control Clinic</title></head>
<body bgcolor="ffffff" text="000044" link="0000ff" vlink="660099">
<center>

<IMG SRC="ccl3.gif" ALT="The New Driver Car Control Clinic">
<H1>
1 in 4 Teens Will Crash<BR>In Their First Year of Driving.
<BR>Will Yours Be The One?</H1><P>
<P><IMG SRC="redbar2.GIF" ALT="----------------------"><P>

<H2>Discover This Revolutionary Exercise Program<BR> To Help Parents Make Their New Drivers <EM>Safer</EM> Drivers </H2>

<table><TR><TD><IMG SRC="SPREAD3.GIF" alt="o"><BR>
56-page Easy-to-use Workbook</td>
<td><IMG SRC="PRODUCT3.GIF" alt="o"><BR>45-minute Instructional Video <BR>on How To Work With<BR> Your New Driver</td><td><IMG SRC="DIAGRAM.GIF" alt="o"><BR>Detailed Course Diagrams and Step-by-Step Instructions </td></tr></table><P>

<h3><IMG SRC="redball2.GIF" alt="--"> Driver Training <IMG SRC="redball2.GIF" alt="--"> Eye Management <br><IMG SRC="redball2.GIF" alt="--"> Brake Management <IMG SRC="redball2.GIF" alt="--"> Defensive Driving<br><IMG SRC="redball2.GIF" alt="--"> Steering Management <IMG SRC="redball2.GIF" alt="--">  Accident-Avoidance Maneuvers <P></h3>
</center>
